    public class RegexFieldDetailView
extends SystemConfigInlineView<RegexFieldDetailPresenter>
    Shows the view of Regex Field section of the Regex Builder dialog.This view provides input text options for generating regex pattern.
    Version:
    1.0 $LastChangedDate:$
    $LastChangedRevision:$
